         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot. Garden ¶ 17/3/72 ¶  ¶ It is really very kind of you, dear Mr Montefiore to think of me so generously and so attentively. I wished I had many sterling friends like you. The photograms I ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">72.03.17</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Eliezer Montefiore</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">MS MS SEQUENCE, Australian Box 4/1, State Library of Victoria, Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS bears M's proposed baronial letterhead (see Home (2017)).</p>
               </note>Melbourne bot. Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">17/3/72</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is really very kind of you, dear Mr Montefiore to think of me so generously and so attentively. I wished I had many sterling friends like you. The photograms I treasure much not only for their artistic value but also on account of the liberality of the donor.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am still harrassed in my Department so pray, do pardon the briefness of the present note. With best remembrances of you &amp; your kind family.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller</p>
         </div>
